{"tid":2125238,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國中止與中港學者交流計劃　逾1700人聯署反對","createTime":"2020-07-26T05:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T05:22:53.000Z","uid":51665,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d04faa9a5312734bdede1a0e6144ed4b97089fe","tid":2125238,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200726/bkn-20200726114016236-0726_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200726%2Fbkn-20200726114016236-0726_00952_001.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLr0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=7a5d53f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200726/bkn-20200726114016236-0726_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200726/photo/bkn-20200726114016236-0726_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200726124727\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200726%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200726114016236-0726_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200726124727&h=87b08b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普本月中旬簽署行政命令，終止對香港的優惠待遇，包括與中國內地和香港學生及學者的「富布賴特交流計劃」（Fulbright exchange program）。 該計劃的成員與曾受惠學者日前發起反對項目中止請願，至今獲超過1700人簽名支持。成員表示，鑑於中美關係現況，反而更需要計劃而非中止。<br />\n有報道指，美國國務院近日已向準備參加計劃的學者發出電郵，指2020至2021年度交流項目將「無法繼續」，但可申請參加其他國家的項目。<br />\n奧地利富布賴特委員會前負責人約翰遜（Lonnie Johnson），本月16日接受美國傳媒訪問時稱，中美兩國文化交流項目中，如此總統級別的行政干預是「史無前例」。另有報道指，中美富布賴特計劃遭到中止，是繼今年1月取消在華的和平隊項目後，又一個兩國民間交流渠道被關閉。<br />\n美國於1946年設立富布賴特交流計劃，旨在促進國際間在教育、文化和科學等領域的交流，是全球規模最大國際交流計劃之一，至今有逾30萬人參加。中國是首個參與該項目的國家，該項目已在超過160個國家受惠。<br />\n<br />\n你老尾唔俾我入境偷技術係違反基本法＋國安法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d570d6b6fdac84fc611a53a5e166487c7951822f","tid":2125238,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"嗰1700個有幾多係支那嘅先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84583dd76c40f8d17a0ab2631bf1e3ae179a3f7a","tid":2125238,"uid":352564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"你比人偷野關我撚事喎，係人地本事你冇本事，好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27445fcf58786b8ba4349c19a9740f09ae1af596","tid":2125238,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"good<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4e343aa08735310e654387524dd3217da09024","tid":2125238,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"請埋呢1700人離開美國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}